text: Fyn or FYN may refer to: * Fyn, or Funen, Denmark * FYN, encoding the proto- oncogene tyrosine-protein kinase Fyn * Freshwater, Yarmouth and Newport Railway, a defunct railway of England * Fuyun Koktokay Airport, in Xinjiang, China * Federal Yugoslav Navy, the navy of the Federal Republic of Yugoslavia
title: Fyn (disambiguation)
